titles.title: A resolution honoring the bicentennial of the City of Astoria.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary: 5/19/2011--Passed Senate without amendment. Expresses the sense of the Senate that: (1) the bicentennial of the City of Astoria, Oregon, should be observed and celebrated, and (2) the people of Astoria should be thanked for their contributions to Oregon and the United States.
